title: Fearless waitress drags gigantic lizard outside Australian restaurant like a pro
text:
The badass in question – 25-year-old Samia Lila – whisked the scary-looking reptile by its tail even as diners could be heard shrieking and hooting in the video clip. (Credit: Facebook) A woman working as a waitress for a restaurant in Australia has proved that she has nerves made of pure steel after she dragged a huge goanna monitor lizard out of her workplace like it was no big deal. The video footage of her feat has since then gone viral and even got her dubbed as the “Goanna Girl”.
The badass in question – 25-year-old Samia Lila – whisked the scary-looking reptile by its tail even as diners could be heard shrieking and hooting in the video clip.
